snippet: Shavonte Zellous scored 11 of her 22 points, a season high, in the final five minutes to help Indiana beat the Liberty in the final game of the regular season for both teams.
abstract: Indiana Fever defeats New York Liberty, 81-76, in final game of regular season for both teams.
